    "Given a requirement, developers usually first gather relevant knowledge, then find and modify existing programs to meet the requirement, and finally verify programs with the assistance of tools.",
    "To mimic this process, we develop several programming tools that are specifically designed for LLMs.",
    "CODEAGENT incorporates these external tools from three perspectives: information retrieval, code implementation, and code testing, which are commonly used by programmers in their daily work.",
